<td id="D6BD64CBEE54B67F0674DC578FD9CFA9" align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="528" valign="top">
2. Krone 5-8 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken id="7D3D9C3665287EC3B8DFED7192C7CA2A" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
25-70 
<normalizedToken id="F771F262E03D3FDB4C07078E4FAD03F4" originalValue="blütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">bluetig</normalizedToken>
, 2-10 cm lang (ohne Stiel).
